CustomFunction.Calculation:
// BeginsWith ( someText; prefixText )
// version 1.1, Daniel A. Shockley, NYHTC

/*
	Determine if the someText begins with prefixText


HISTORY:
	1.1 - 2016-09-29 ( eshagdar ): updated documentation.
	1.0 - 201x-xx-xx ( dshockley ): first created.
*/


Left ( someText; Length( prefixText ) ) = prefixText
